1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:02,010
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,010 --> 00:00:03,610
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,610 --> 00:00:05,180
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,210 --> 00:00:08,680
Hello? What is it?

5
00:00:09,880 --> 00:00:11,250
It was Chairman Park Tae Ho.

6
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:15,120
Chairman Park
falsified the test results.

7
00:00:16,420 --> 00:00:19,190
The bloodstain on the pearl
was Chairman Park's.

8
00:00:21,260 --> 00:00:22,960
The one who murdered your sister...

9
00:00:24,700 --> 00:00:25,830
was Park Tae Ho.

10
00:00:29,470 --> 00:00:30,470
What?

11
00:00:32,470 --> 00:00:33,810
It was Park Tae Ho?

12
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:42,680
It appears that Kim Myung Hui died,

13
00:00:43,210 --> 00:00:45,120
and it was Kim Dan Hui
who showed up instead.

14
00:00:46,850 --> 00:00:47,850
Am I wrong?

15
00:00:49,690 --> 00:00:51,660
After all, you and I
both know very well...

16
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:55,160
that Kim Myung Hui
and Kim Dan Hui...

17
00:00:56,190 --> 00:00:57,260
are twins.

18
00:00:57,960 --> 00:01:00,900
What exactly are you getting at?

19
00:01:01,700 --> 00:01:05,570
I think the real Kim Myung Hui died
back then.

20
00:01:06,270 --> 00:01:10,610
What if she wasn't poisoned,
but strangled to death instead?

21
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:15,880
And the person
who strangled her to death...

22
00:01:18,420 --> 00:01:19,420
It was you, wasn't it?

23
00:01:30,230 --> 00:01:32,630
I thought you were just
some money-grubbing punk,

24
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:34,570
but I'm impressed.

25
00:01:36,370 --> 00:01:37,370
Detective Yun.

26
00:01:39,170 --> 00:01:40,170
That's right.

27
00:01:42,070 --> 00:01:44,140
I killed Kim Myung Hui.

28
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,350
Park Tae Ho...

29
00:01:57,960 --> 00:02:00,260
Park Tae Ho killed my sister.

30
00:02:01,860 --> 00:02:03,030
It was Park Tae Ho.

31
00:02:15,410 --> 00:02:19,480
What in the world happened that day,
30 years ago?

32
00:02:20,010 --> 00:02:21,580
Oh Jung Ran and Kim Myung Hui.

33
00:02:22,380 --> 00:02:26,050
I mean, Kim Dan Hui.
They still don't know anything.

34
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:31,260
You must've looked into
the whole situation, right?

35
00:03:56,010 --> 00:03:57,880
Why is the bottle full?

36
00:03:58,940 --> 00:04:00,710
I'm sure I drank some earlier.

37
00:04:01,750 --> 00:04:02,780
Something's not right.

38
00:04:16,930 --> 00:04:19,300
Honey. I...

39
00:04:22,030 --> 00:04:23,030
I...

40
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:28,010
I had no idea you were coming.

41
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:40,790
The baby is due soon.

42
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:44,760
I was just getting
some things ready.

43
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,830
Getting your hospital go-bag ready?

44
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:56,630
Is that why you sold this?

45
00:05:02,610 --> 00:05:05,280
Around here, from the jewelers...

46
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:07,610
down to the pawn shops,

47
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:09,750
if any Adele jewelry comes in,

48
00:05:12,150 --> 00:05:14,290
they contact me, no questions asked.

49
00:05:14,950 --> 00:05:17,690
To make sure our Adele jewelry...

50
00:05:17,690 --> 00:05:19,720
isn't just floating around
the low-end market,

51
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:24,100
I've been keeping tabs on it.

52
00:05:27,370 --> 00:05:30,940
You dare sell a gift I gave you...

53
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:34,010
to stab me in the back?

54
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:38,780
I told you clearly
that I was leaving.

55
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,450
I never gave you permission!

56
00:05:40,450 --> 00:05:42,610
I don't need it.

57
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,320
Get back here!

58
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:03,700
You said you trusted me.

59
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:06,340
Since you decided to trust me,

60
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:09,270
and since you promised
we'd be a family,

61
00:06:09,970 --> 00:06:11,910
you should've kept that promise.

62
00:06:12,110 --> 00:06:15,280
You already have a family.

63
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:18,180
It isn't a family
if there's no love!

64
00:06:18,620 --> 00:06:21,190
I know your wife is pregnant.

65
00:06:22,250 --> 00:06:25,160
You should protect your own family.

66
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:28,530
It's greedy to think
you can have us both.

67
00:06:28,990 --> 00:06:32,060
Before your greed
makes everyone miserable,

68
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:34,300
I'm choosing to leave first.

69
00:06:34,930 --> 00:06:37,640
Myung Hui, no!

70
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:40,300
- Let go. Let go of me!
- Myung Hui.

71
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:54,090
How dare you turn your back on me
and betray me?

72
00:06:54,690 --> 00:06:57,360
You're just like my parents
who abandoned me.

73
00:06:58,190 --> 00:07:01,490
That's right.
You never trusted or loved me.

74
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,960
You only ever wanted my money.

75
00:07:10,170 --> 00:07:14,040
You're the greedy one, not me!

76
00:07:15,710 --> 00:07:16,870
It's not me.

77
00:07:42,530 --> 00:07:44,970
Kim Myung Hui.

78
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:47,940
Myung Hui.

79
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:02,490
Adele... My Adele...

80
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:05,820
My Adele could be ruined.

81
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:21,800
Hey.

82
00:09:22,370 --> 00:09:23,370
Hey...

83
00:09:32,810 --> 00:09:34,580
I think she's dead, Jung Ran!

84
00:09:34,980 --> 00:09:36,110
Never mind that.

85
00:09:36,850 --> 00:09:38,450
Just clean up this broken bottle.

86
00:09:40,050 --> 00:09:41,150
Why?

87
00:09:41,890 --> 00:09:44,290
Because it's proof
that I poisoned her.

88
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,530
Then...

89
00:09:48,430 --> 00:09:49,730
It was you?

90
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:53,760
You heard me. Get moving.

91
00:10:09,410 --> 00:10:11,320
Don't think this is unfair.

92
00:10:13,850 --> 00:10:17,020
It's only natural for a mother
to protect her child.

93
00:10:26,260 --> 00:10:27,300
I...

94
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:32,140
even poisoned the lady
who took me in.

95
00:10:33,140 --> 00:10:34,640
Park Tae Ho's wife...

96
00:10:35,940 --> 00:10:37,010
No, that's not it.

97
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:42,850
I desperately wanted to be the lady
of the Adele Group, you see.

98
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:48,050
Now, my child will be the sole heir
to the Adele Group.

99
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:53,890
I've killed for a place
in the golden castle,

100
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:56,630
and I can't let anyone steal it.

101
00:11:40,170 --> 00:11:41,170
Myung Hui?

102
00:11:46,940 --> 00:11:47,950
Myung Hui!

103
00:11:49,810 --> 00:11:52,380
Myung Hui, come on. Wake up!

104
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:54,950
Myung Hui, what's wrong?

105
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:57,350
Myung Hui!

106
00:11:58,660 --> 00:12:00,590
Myung Hui!

107
00:12:01,060 --> 00:12:02,360
Oh no, what do we do?

108
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:21,110
The reason I'm telling you this...

109
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:24,850
is because you're an accomplice.

110
00:12:25,420 --> 00:12:26,650
An accomplice?

111
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:28,350
While I was cleaning up the mess,

112
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:31,020
you took my money.

113
00:12:31,020 --> 00:12:32,660
In my ledger,

114
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:37,530
there's a record
of the payment I made to you.

115
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:43,870
That's why you should never
take money so carelessly.

116
00:12:47,470 --> 00:12:49,310
You've made it
to a high-ranking position.

117
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:55,550
If you want to keep it,
you need to shut your mouth.

118
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:07,690
A murderer thinks
he can threaten a cop?

119
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:11,000
Darn it.

120
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:22,140
He killed...

121
00:13:23,210 --> 00:13:24,580
my sister.

122
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:29,150
Park Tae Ho...

123
00:13:30,210 --> 00:13:31,480
killed her.

124
00:14:44,460 --> 00:14:45,560
Kim Myung Hui.

125
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:50,260
Where is she and what is she doing?

126
00:14:50,890 --> 00:14:52,160
Good grief.

127
00:15:20,190 --> 00:15:23,990
I got to my mother.
Thanks for your concern.

128
00:15:24,300 --> 00:15:26,200
Is she all right?

129
00:15:28,800 --> 00:15:30,030
She's too quiet.

130
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:32,300
That actually worries me more.

131
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:41,250
Don't you also want this child
and want to keep him safe?

132
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:45,580
Then please accept me
along with our child.

133
00:15:46,650 --> 00:15:49,850
Let me live by your side
as this child's mother.

134
00:15:50,350 --> 00:15:51,590
Park Tae Ho.

135
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:55,190
He played dumb
after killing my sister.

136
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,590
I had something urgent to attend to.

137
00:15:58,460 --> 00:15:59,900
I'll head to my room, then.

138
00:16:00,730 --> 00:16:01,800
Myung Hui.

139
00:16:02,100 --> 00:16:03,330
Come...

140
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:05,140
to my room tonight.

141
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,910
All right.

142
00:16:11,180 --> 00:16:14,010
Not knowing he was the man
who killed my sister,

143
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:17,650
I lived with my enemy for 30 years.

144
00:16:19,050 --> 00:16:20,450
(Application for Divorce
by Mutual Consent)

145
00:16:21,150 --> 00:16:22,150
Darn you!

146
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:23,990
Are you crazy?

147
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:25,390
And it all starts...

148
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:28,030
with you losing your position
at Adele Group.

149
00:16:28,530 --> 00:16:31,100
I wasted 30 years
living like a fool,

150
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:33,300
fighting a pointless battle
against Oh Jung Ran.

151
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:41,540
Sir!

152
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:46,910
I should've killed him.

153
00:16:49,710 --> 00:16:51,420
I should've just killed him.

154
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:00,860
Instead,

155
00:17:01,430 --> 00:17:03,730
I saved that man's life.

156
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:05,500
I...

157
00:17:06,430 --> 00:17:09,870
Me, of all people...
I saved Park Tae Ho's life!

158
00:17:11,770 --> 00:17:16,640
Mother, it's okay.

159
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:22,710
This can't be happening.

160
00:17:23,710 --> 00:17:25,780
I can't believe
I was used and fooled...

161
00:17:26,150 --> 00:17:28,020
by the very man
who killed my sister!

162
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:32,060
The past 30 years of my life...

163
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:36,490
feel so miserable and pathetic.

164
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:41,300
More than I hate Park Tae Ho,

165
00:17:42,770 --> 00:17:46,270
I can't stand myself
for playing into his game.

166
00:17:46,700 --> 00:17:47,770
I...

167
00:17:50,210 --> 00:17:52,040
I don't deserve to be your mother.

168
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:53,240
That's not true.

169
00:17:54,650 --> 00:17:57,280
That's not true, Mother. You...

170
00:17:57,610 --> 00:17:59,780
- did nothing wrong.
- No!

171
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,450
I failed at everything.

172
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:08,390
My revenge. My life.

173
00:18:09,090 --> 00:18:10,430
I've ruined it all.

174
00:18:12,760 --> 00:18:16,900
I spent 30 years struggling,
and I've got nothing to show for it.

175
00:18:17,270 --> 00:18:18,270
Mother.

176
00:18:18,770 --> 00:18:21,370
Mother!
You still have me, don't you?

177
00:18:24,910 --> 00:18:26,640
I'm your life.

178
00:18:27,610 --> 00:18:29,550
I represent
those 30 years of your life.

179
00:18:29,550 --> 00:18:31,480
You're the reason I'm alive today.

180
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:33,550
Even when you faced
all kinds of humiliation,

181
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:35,290
you protected me.

182
00:18:37,860 --> 00:18:39,190
In your life,

183
00:18:40,290 --> 00:18:41,790
I was there too.

184
00:18:48,630 --> 00:18:50,000
I'm sorry.

185
00:18:54,470 --> 00:18:56,140
You must be having a hard time too.

186
00:19:01,810 --> 00:19:03,050
You must be...

187
00:19:04,550 --> 00:19:07,150
in just as much pain
as I am right now.

188
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:13,790
I'm okay.

189
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:17,290
If you're okay,

190
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:19,730
then I'm okay too.

191
00:19:22,500 --> 00:19:23,500
You're right.

192
00:19:26,370 --> 00:19:27,440
I had...

193
00:19:28,670 --> 00:19:29,910
you.

194
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:34,140
So that I wouldn't be left all alone
in this world,

195
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:38,880
my sister sent you to me.

196
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:42,820
I had...

197
00:19:43,820 --> 00:19:45,920
my sister and you.

198
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:14,890
I'm sorry.

199
00:20:15,220 --> 00:20:16,220
I don't have...

200
00:20:16,850 --> 00:20:19,220
any intention of getting
between you and Jin Ju.

201
00:20:20,560 --> 00:20:22,760
Let me know
when you two have a plan.

202
00:20:27,530 --> 00:20:28,870
Park Min Jun...

203
00:20:29,870 --> 00:20:31,270
That's the kind of guy he is.

204
00:20:41,450 --> 00:20:42,550
The photos.

205
00:20:44,650 --> 00:20:45,680
That was you, wasn't it?

206
00:20:48,020 --> 00:20:49,020
The photos.

207
00:20:49,090 --> 00:20:52,920
I'm pretty sure I warned you
not to mess with Chloe.

208
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:57,760
Did you really think
I'd fall for fake photos like that?

209
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:02,970
How can you be so sure they're fake?

210
00:21:02,970 --> 00:21:05,040
Because I know Park Min Jun.

211
00:21:05,840 --> 00:21:07,700
He's an annoying jerk,

212
00:21:08,140 --> 00:21:11,170
but he's not one to end up
in questionable photos with Chloe.

213
00:21:12,110 --> 00:21:13,410
The same goes for her.

214
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:17,580
You trust them that much?

215
00:21:28,890 --> 00:21:30,160
Everyone...

216
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:33,560
wants Chloe and me to break up,
but what about you?

217
00:21:33,900 --> 00:21:34,900
What's your angle?

218
00:21:38,770 --> 00:21:41,300
Don't tell me it's me you're after.

219
00:21:46,380 --> 00:21:48,650
That would really disgust me.

220
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:51,520
What?

221
00:21:52,550 --> 00:21:53,550
Disgust you?

222
00:21:54,250 --> 00:21:55,250
Hey,

223
00:21:55,850 --> 00:21:57,690
just because
I let you blackmail me for a bit...

224
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:59,960
doesn't mean you have
any power here.

225
00:22:00,020 --> 00:22:01,590
Wake up.

226
00:22:02,130 --> 00:22:03,490
You're nothing.

227
00:22:04,360 --> 00:22:05,760
And you're definitely not someone...

228
00:22:08,470 --> 00:22:10,230
I ever want to be with.

229
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:21,240
You're clearly mistaken here too.

230
00:22:22,850 --> 00:22:26,380
Min Jun and Chloe could betray you
at any time, you know.

231
00:22:28,950 --> 00:22:32,020
I'll show you exactly
what a nobody like me can do.

232
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:35,760
Just watch.

233
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:57,680
So, have you found Kim Dan Hui?

234
00:22:58,350 --> 00:23:00,450
We haven't been able to locate her.

235
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:02,190
What about Min Jun? Still nothing?

236
00:23:02,390 --> 00:23:05,590
Yes, sir. He's still unreachable.

237
00:23:06,290 --> 00:23:08,530
Could the two of them be together?

238
00:23:10,790 --> 00:23:13,230
You don't think she found out
about the lab, do you?

239
00:23:14,330 --> 00:23:17,500
Of course not. I made sure
that lab tech stays quiet.

240
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:20,970
Do you still not know
how Kim Dan Hui obtained...

241
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:23,170
that blood evidence...

242
00:23:24,310 --> 00:23:25,910
- from 30 years ago?
- No, sir.

243
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:29,750
All I know is that Secretary Jung
requested the DNA test.

244
00:23:29,850 --> 00:23:32,450
Just focus
on finding Kim Dan Hui for now.

245
00:23:32,850 --> 00:23:36,550
She went out to take a phone call
and completely vanished.

246
00:23:36,950 --> 00:23:39,460
Check the restaurant's
security cameras.

247
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:41,860
I've already requested it
from the restaurant,

248
00:23:41,930 --> 00:23:43,060
but the owner is away.

249
00:23:43,430 --> 00:23:46,460
I'll get the security footage
as soon as I can reach them.

250
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:48,930
Don't wait. Get it now.

251
00:23:49,570 --> 00:23:52,040
Use bribes, threats,
whatever it takes.

252
00:23:52,300 --> 00:23:53,970
Yes, sir.

253
00:23:58,680 --> 00:24:00,840
Kim Dan Hui. Could she have...

254
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:04,180
overheard my conversation...

255
00:24:05,020 --> 00:24:06,020
with Detective Yun?

256
00:24:15,390 --> 00:24:16,390
Dan Hui.

257
00:24:17,260 --> 00:24:19,400
Let's not cry anymore.

258
00:24:19,700 --> 00:24:22,270
If we cry,
it's like letting that monster win.

259
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:24,840
From now on,

260
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:27,000
I'm never going to cry again.

261
00:24:29,570 --> 00:24:30,570
You're right.

262
00:24:32,010 --> 00:24:33,240
Let's do that.

263
00:24:37,110 --> 00:24:38,320
No mother...

264
00:24:39,050 --> 00:24:40,950
just sits around
crying her eyes out.

265
00:24:41,450 --> 00:24:43,390
Don't overthink this.

266
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:45,190
That monster, Park Tae Ho...

267
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:48,190
Just focus on
how you're going to tear him apart.

268
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:53,160
He may be the chairman,
but it's 3 against 1.

269
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:56,700
In fact, everyone else out there...

270
00:24:57,570 --> 00:24:59,070
is on your side too, Dan Hui.

271
00:25:13,850 --> 00:25:18,190
Park Tae Ho, that monster!
I swear he's not human.

272
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:20,820
How could he do that to the woman
carrying his own child?

273
00:25:21,490 --> 00:25:24,190
He then treated Dan Hui like that,
knowing all along she was her twin.

274
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:26,830
There probably isn't a higher power,

275
00:25:26,830 --> 00:25:29,330
seeing how that monster
is still alive.

276
00:25:29,800 --> 00:25:31,130
Tell me about it.

277
00:25:31,470 --> 00:25:34,800
Park Tae Ho didn't just kill
Kim Myung Hui.

278
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:37,640
He basically killed Kim Dan Hui too.

279
00:25:38,110 --> 00:25:41,440
Jin Ju, it's a good thing you were
suspicious and kept digging.

280
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:43,710
At least we finally know the truth.

281
00:25:43,910 --> 00:25:44,920
That Park Tae Ho...

282
00:25:45,180 --> 00:25:47,250
really would've gone
his whole life...

283
00:25:47,450 --> 00:25:48,790
getting away with his lies.

284
00:25:48,990 --> 00:25:50,120
Now,

285
00:25:50,650 --> 00:25:53,190
it looks like Ms. Kim and I have
the same goal.

286
00:25:54,390 --> 00:25:57,690
Taking down Park Tae Ho.

287
00:26:09,410 --> 00:26:10,470
Are you okay?

288
00:26:12,210 --> 00:26:14,950
I know this isn't easy,
but hang in there.

289
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:17,580
I know words of comfort...

290
00:26:17,980 --> 00:26:20,320
probably don't mean much
to you right now.

291
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:24,390
Pull yourself together
and be there for your mother.

292
00:26:24,990 --> 00:26:25,990
Right.

293
00:26:29,130 --> 00:26:32,530
My mother protected me for 30 years,

294
00:26:33,530 --> 00:26:34,930
so now it's my turn.

295
00:26:35,770 --> 00:26:37,900
First, I should go home
and face my father...

296
00:26:41,910 --> 00:26:43,240
I mean, Park Tae Ho.

297
00:26:44,510 --> 00:26:45,740
I have to face him, right?

298
00:26:46,710 --> 00:26:50,450
Yes. He's probably looking
for Ms. Kim by now.

299
00:26:50,810 --> 00:26:53,320
He might be suspicious
since she suddenly disappeared,

300
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:55,950
so you need to buy her some time
with a good excuse.

301
00:26:56,890 --> 00:26:59,760
My sister and I can cover for her.

302
00:27:00,060 --> 00:27:03,030
We can just say something happened
and that we're looking after her.

303
00:27:03,090 --> 00:27:06,060
Okay, let's try that for now.

304
00:27:06,060 --> 00:27:07,230
Can you...

305
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:11,100
look after my mother for me?

306
00:27:11,100 --> 00:27:14,270
Of course. Don't worry
about things here and get going.

307
00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:15,940
Thank you.

308
00:27:43,270 --> 00:27:44,270
You.

309
00:27:45,070 --> 00:27:46,240
What's going on?

310
00:27:46,970 --> 00:27:49,810
Why didn't you show up for dinner,
and why haven't you been picking up?

311
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:51,810
Your mother isn't answering either.

312
00:27:52,380 --> 00:27:53,910
Were you two together?

313
00:27:57,910 --> 00:27:59,120
You murderer.

314
00:28:00,280 --> 00:28:04,220
You killed Jin Ju's father,
and even my birth mother.

315
00:28:04,550 --> 00:28:06,820
As if that wasn't enough,
for 30 years,

316
00:28:08,190 --> 00:28:10,590
you deceived and used my mother.

317
00:28:11,430 --> 00:28:12,460
You...

318
00:28:13,330 --> 00:28:15,170
are not my father anymore.

319
00:28:15,970 --> 00:28:18,540
I will destroy you.

320
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:22,540
I asked you a question.

321
00:28:24,670 --> 00:28:25,680
Mother is...

322
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:28,680
Sir! Sir.

323
00:28:29,110 --> 00:28:31,110
I've secured
the restaurant's CCTV footage.

324
00:28:31,110 --> 00:28:32,120
What?

325
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:36,590
I think you should see it
for yourself.

326
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:39,560
- Fine. Come with me.
- Yes, sir.

327
00:28:50,730 --> 00:28:52,200
We have a problem.

328
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:57,110
Manager Kang brought
the CCTV footage...

329
00:28:57,210 --> 00:28:58,240
from the restaurant.

330
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:02,250
They wouldn't give us...

331
00:29:02,250 --> 00:29:04,510
the indoor footage to protect
other customers' privacy,

332
00:29:04,980 --> 00:29:07,420
so I only managed
to get the garden footage.

333
00:29:16,290 --> 00:29:19,000
Kim Dan Hui heard everything.
Find her, fast!

334
00:29:19,300 --> 00:29:21,700
She might have gone
to Secretary Jung's place,

335
00:29:21,900 --> 00:29:23,070
so search there first.

336
00:29:23,130 --> 00:29:24,130
Yes, sir.

337
00:29:27,870 --> 00:29:31,740
Did Kim Dan Hui
finally figure everything out?

338
00:29:32,310 --> 00:29:33,680
I need to find her fast...

339
00:29:33,940 --> 00:29:37,250
and handle this
before she tries anything.

340
00:29:40,580 --> 00:29:43,890
What are you talking about?
Kim Myung Hui is Kim Dan Hui?

341
00:29:44,290 --> 00:29:47,320
And Park Tae Ho
killed Kim Myung Hui?

342
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:51,330
You told me to tail Detective Yun,
so I did.

343
00:29:51,490 --> 00:29:52,600
I heard it loud and clear...

344
00:29:53,900 --> 00:29:55,670
with my own two ears.

345
00:30:10,610 --> 00:30:13,320
So, Park Tae Ho...

346
00:30:14,180 --> 00:30:15,820
killed Kim Myung Hui.

347
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,450
And her twin sister, Kim Dan Hui,

348
00:30:17,520 --> 00:30:19,120
pretended to be Kim Myung Hui...

349
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:21,720
to get revenge for her sister?

350
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:23,530
Yes, exactly!

351
00:30:24,460 --> 00:30:26,900
My heart was pounding
the whole way here.

352
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:28,230
It was nerve-racking.

353
00:30:28,970 --> 00:30:30,370
What the...

354
00:30:31,130 --> 00:30:32,300
Park Tae Ho...

355
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:35,740
knew the whole time
and just played dumb for 30 years?

356
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:39,140
Even you must think
he was too cruel to Ms. Kim.

357
00:30:40,580 --> 00:30:43,450
No, I'm talking about me.

358
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:45,580
How could he do this to me?

359
00:30:46,220 --> 00:30:47,250
To you?

360
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:51,820
Do you think Kim Myung Hui,
I mean, Kim Dan Hui,

361
00:30:51,820 --> 00:30:53,120
was the only one he toyed with?

362
00:30:53,520 --> 00:30:56,090
He killed her
and then framed me for it.

363
00:30:56,560 --> 00:30:58,730
He just stood by and watched...

364
00:30:58,730 --> 00:31:00,900
while Kim Dan Hui tormented me
to get her revenge.

365
00:31:01,430 --> 00:31:05,270
In fact, he even used me
to egg her on.

366
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:07,140
Now that you mention it,
you're right.

367
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:09,240
Someone else killed her sister,

368
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:12,640
but you've been suffering
all this time unfairly.

369
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:16,210
Exactly. For 30 years,

370
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:18,410
I've been a puppet
in Park Tae Ho's hands.

371
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:20,780
That crazy jerk!

372
00:31:22,950 --> 00:31:23,950
Darn.

373
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:35,630
What? You searched all night
and still couldn't find her?

374
00:31:36,470 --> 00:31:38,840
Check the CCTV footage
around the restaurant...

375
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:40,700
and find out where she went.

376
00:31:43,410 --> 00:31:46,080
Park Min Jun,
get down here right now!

377
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:48,880
Is something wrong?

378
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:53,050
This has nothing to do with you,
so stay out of it.

379
00:31:53,420 --> 00:31:54,450
Nothing to do with me?

380
00:31:56,420 --> 00:31:57,420
Right.

381
00:31:58,290 --> 00:32:00,190
You've always ignored me anyway.

382
00:32:05,130 --> 00:32:06,130
Kim Myung Hui.

383
00:32:10,900 --> 00:32:13,070
You... Where have you been?

384
00:32:48,970 --> 00:32:51,770
(Pearl in Red)

385
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:53,810
Kim Myung Hui, you!

386
00:32:54,080 --> 00:32:55,180
Shut your mouth!

387
00:32:55,180 --> 00:32:58,250
Keep my sister's name
out of your filthy mouth.

388
00:32:58,310 --> 00:33:00,620
Is it true that you murdered
the woman carrying your son?

389
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:02,120
Where is Kim Dan Hui now?

390
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:06,120
- Everyone, it's all lies.
- Father!

391
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:09,430
The truth is finally out.

392
00:33:09,890 --> 00:33:12,500
The truth about Park Tae Ho
and Kim Dan Hui.

393
00:33:12,660 --> 00:33:15,600
I think it's time for us
to make our move.

394
00:33:16,130 --> 00:33:18,030
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
